
##  Progress Updates (2026-01)

### NAS Build & Storage Lab Update

This project documents my home NAS setup and what I have configured so far.

**Hardware**
- Synology 4-bay NAS
- 2.5GbE, 10-port unmanaged switch

**Users & Permissions**
- Created multiple users
- Configured upload and delete permissions
- Enabled SMB sharing across devices

**Storage Protection**
- Scheduled SMART quick checks weekly
- Scheduled deep scans monthly
- Alerts configured for any drive health concerns

**Snapshot & Replication**
- Automated snapshot schedules enabled
- Replication configured for versioned recovery

**Backing Up**
- Next step: automate backups to Backblaze B2 and Glacier with redundancy across availability zones

**Ongoing Work**
- Monitoring integration (Wazuh)
- Vulnerability scanning (Nessus/Tenable)
- Lab automation and containerization

Next planned updates will include screenshots, configs, and scripts.

